# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者賭博嗰陣，為咗避免蝕太多錢，而將手上嘅股票或者注碼賣出嚟減低損失嘅行為。
eng:to stop a loss; to cut losses
<eg>
yue:隻股票跌到呢個價錢，你應該要止蝕離場。 (zek3 gu2 piao4 dit3 dou3 ni1 go3 gaa3 cin2, nei5 jing1 goi1 jiu3 zi2 sik1 lei4 coeng4.)
eng:You should cut your losses and leave the market as the stock has fallen to this price. [end of text]


